odb4py

This product includes software developed at the
European Centre for Medium-Range Weather Forecasts (ECMWF).

Portions of this software are derived from the ECMWF ODB (Observation DataBase) API bundle.

Original ODB software:
Copyright (C) ECMWF.
All rights reserved.

Modifications and adaptations have been made in odb4py
to provide a Python C-extension interface and a reduced
runtime suitable for distribution as Python wheels.

These modifications include:
 - pruning unused components of the ODB API bundle
 - integration into a Python C extension
 - build system redesign using CMake and scikit-build
 - runtime packaging for manylinux compatibility

The original ODB software remains property of ECMWF
and its respective contributors.
